categories: Category:Star Wars: The Clone Wars voice actors

nodes.text: Donald Adeosun Faison (born June 22, 1974) is an actor, comedian and voice actor who provides the voice of Hype Fazon in Star Wars Resistance, as well as that of the super tactical droid in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars episode "Old Friends Not Forgotten". He previously appeared in Robot Chicken: Star Wars Episode II and the unreleased Star Wars Detours.
